text: LSU vs. Florida live stream, TV schedule: Where to watch the Tigers and Gators Saturday Leonard Fournette FILE - In this Sept. 26, 2015, file photo, LSU running back Leonard Fournette (7) gets past Syracuse cornerback Wayne Morgan (2) for a touchdown in the first half of an NCAA college football game, in Syracuse, N.Y. It might be the matchup of the season: LSU running back Leonard Fournette, perhaps the nation's best player vs. Florida's vaunted defense. The No. 6 Tigers and No. 8 Gators meet in prime time Saturday in a game between unbeaten teams. (AP Photo/Mike Groll, File)
